Dialogue: 0,0:00:06.44,0:00:09.57,Default,,0,0,0,,3ª Guerra Mundial.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:09.57,0:00:10.53,Default,,0,0,0,,{\move(640,680,640,620,66,400)}Em 2036,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:10.53,0:00:16.20,Default,,0,0,0,,{\pos(640,620)}ela será o resultado de 5.7 bilhões de vítimas no mundo todo.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:16.20,0:00:17.62,Default,,0,0,0,,{\pos(640,620)}E é isto que a inicia.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:18.37,0:00:20.37,Default,,0,0,0,,{\move(640,620,640,680,1276,1735)}Hã? O que é isso?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:20.37,0:00:22.04,Default,,0,0,0,,É algum tipo de robô?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:22.04,0:00:23.79,Default,,0,0,0,,Ele se transforma ou algo do tipo?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:23.79,0:00:25.92,Default,,0,0,0,,Uma máquina do tempo.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:25.92,0:00:27.38,Default,,0,0,0,,Sério?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:27.38,0:00:30.92,Default,,0,0,0,,Sabia que a reconheceria, Tio.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:30.92,0:00:32.72,Default,,0,0,0,,Isso torna as coisas mais fáceis.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:33.30,0:00:35.13,Default,,0,0,0,,Venha comigo.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:39.60,0:00:40.85,Default,,0,0,0,,Me recuso.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:41.98,0:00:43.69,Default,,0,0,0,,Okarin?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:43.69,0:00:46.56,Default,,0,0,0,,Vim até aqui através da linha do tempo do mundo Alfa.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:47.31,0:00:48.77,Default,,0,0,0,,Ao longo das três últimas semanas,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:48.77,0:00:51.23,Default,,0,0,0,,saltei pelas linhas temporais de novo e de novo,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:51.23,0:00:55.57,Default,,0,0,0,,sacrificando Kurisu em prol de retornar à linha de tempo do mundo Beta.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:55.57,0:01:00.79,Default,,0,0,0,,Não deixarei que isso tudo tenha sido em vão!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:00.79,0:01:02.75,Default,,0,0,0,,Kurisu?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:03.71,0:01:05.16,Default,,0,0,0,,Kurisu?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:06.54,0:01:09.04,Default,,0,0,0,,Não era o nome daquela cientista
Dialogue: 0,0:01:09.04,0:01:11.09,Default,,0,0,0,,que foi esfaqueada na Rádio Kaikan?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:14.51,0:01:15.84,Default,,0,0,0,,Okabe Rintarou,
Dialogue: 0,0:01:16.59,0:01:20.51,Default,,0,0,0,,e se eu te dissesse que para impedir a 3ª Guerra Mundial
Dialogue: 0,0:01:20.51,0:01:23.81,Default,,0,0,0,,é preciso que, em 28 de Julho de 2010,
Dialogue: 0,0:01:24.23,0:01:27.02,Default,,0,0,0,,a morte de Makise Kurisu seja evitada?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:29.90,0:01:31.02,Default,,0,0,0,,O que quer dizer?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:31.02,0:01:33.28,Default,,0,0,0,,Não sei dos detalhes,
Dialogue: 0,0:01:33.28,0:01:36.57,Default,,0,0,0,,mas tenho uma missão:
Dialogue: 0,0:01:36.57,0:01:38.45,Default,,0,0,0,,Salvar Makise Kurisu
Dialogue: 0,0:01:38.45,0:01:42.70,Default,,0,0,0,,e ir para uma linha de mundo não afetada pelo campo de atração,
Dialogue: 0,0:01:43.16,0:01:45.20,Default,,0,0,0,,o Steins Gate!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:59.47,0:02:05.06,op romaj,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,0)}inochi no shuchou to muimi no shoumei
Dialogue: 0,0:02:05.06,0:02:11.73,op romaj,,0,0,0,,anata ni wa taikutsu shinogi ni taranu kokkei
Dialogue: 0,0:02:11.73,0:02:16.94,op romaj,,0,0,0,,shihaisha kidori no oroka na shuzoku wa
Dialogue: 0,0:02:16.94,0:02:22.87,op romaj,,0,0,0,,unuboreta chisetsu na teiri wo narabeta
Dialogue: 0,0:02:22.87,0:02:28.96,op romaj,,0,0,0,,{"M}mugen{"} to shinjita ai mo sora no kanata mo
Dialogue: 0,0:02:28.96,0:02:34.84,op romaj,,0,0,0,,bokutachi ni shimesareta kasou no jiyuu
Dialogue: 0,0:02:34.84,0:02:40.89,op romaj,,0,0,0,,{"Y}yuugen{"} sore wa mujihi ni toki wo kizami
Dialogue: 0,0:02:40.89,0:02:45.35,op romaj,,0,0,0,,asu sae mo hitei suru sentaku e
Dialogue: 0,0:02:45.35,0:02:47.89,op romaj,,0,0,0,,Hacking to the Gate
Dialogue: 0,0:02:47.89,0:02:54.73,op romaj,,0,0,0,,ikutsu mono kagayakeru hibi nakama to no yakusoku
Dialogue: 0,0:02:54.73,0:02:59.74,op romaj,,0,0,0,,nakatta koto ni wa shite wa ikenai
Dialogue: 0,0:02:59.74,0:03:06.70,op romaj,,0,0,0,,sono tame ni toki wo azamuku nokosareta shikake ni
Dialogue: 0,0:03:06.70,0:03:12.96,op romaj,,0,0,0,,{\fad(0,200)}mou mayoi wa nai kodoku no kansokusha
Dialogue: 0,0:01:59.47,0:02:05.06,op trans,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,0)}Mesmo que os pontos de vista da vida e suas provas sem sentido
Dialogue: 0,0:02:05.06,0:02:11.73,op trans,,0,0,0,,não sejam nada para você e não possam aliviar seu tédio
Dialogue: 0,0:02:11.73,0:02:16.94,op trans,,0,0,0,,As pessoas tolas daquela raça, atuando como líderes
Dialogue: 0,0:02:16.94,0:02:22.87,op trans,,0,0,0,,têm escrito teoremas infantis que fedem à vaidade
Dialogue: 0,0:02:22.87,0:02:28.96,op trans,,0,0,0,,Temos tido a liberdade de imaginar as coisas
Dialogue: 0,0:02:28.96,0:02:34.84,op trans,,0,0,0,,como o amor infinito que está além do céu
Dialogue: 0,0:02:34.84,0:02:40.89,op trans,,0,0,0,,A crueldade finita permite que o tempo flua
Dialogue: 0,0:02:40.89,0:02:45.35,op trans,,0,0,0,,assim dirijo minha escolha para renunciar o amanhã
Dialogue: 0,0:02:45.35,0:02:47.89,op trans,,0,0,0,,Hackeando ao Portão
Dialogue: 0,0:02:47.89,0:02:54.73,op trans,,0,0,0,,Eu não deveria fingir que não fiz promessas
Dialogue: 0,0:02:54.73,0:02:59.74,op trans,,0,0,0,,para voltar com meus amigos para aqueles dias vividos
Dialogue: 0,0:02:59.74,0:03:06.70,op trans,,0,0,0,,Então agora iludirei o próprio tempo com os truques que me restam,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:06.70,0:03:12.96,op trans,,0,0,0,,{\fad(0,200)}assim como sou um observador solitário sem mais dúvida alguma
